Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.69,0:00:36.10,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.30,0:00:48.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.28,0:00:57.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.85,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.89,0:01:14.13,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:20.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.21,0:01:28.05,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四月了 春天到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.69,0:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美我最喜歡春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.46,0:01:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天會開好多花 太陽公公也好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學校也煥然一新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.37,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好多新人進來 還有好多新的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美我最喜歡春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美 快撿球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,球啦 在你後面了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第八話  四月的她」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來、我來～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 你沒事吧 田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 她完全失去意識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把她帶到保健室如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒怎麼樣真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過看來休養一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉讓各位擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 話說回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怎麼來到這裏的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.94,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有看到田邊的表情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連耳根都紅了 好可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她似乎不會排斥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來好像其實對速水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要再說了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼大家都怪怪的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是田邊也有權力選對象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不錯喔 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然看到你受歡迎的一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記寫作業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有作業能給男人抄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 作業借我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給速水學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是一年四班的新井木勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有件事一定要告訴學長 所以才寫了這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我煩惱了很久 不過一直這樣子也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想下定決心說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實 我從以前就對學長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 這應該是情書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年四班 座號三號 新井木勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八月四號出生 獅子座A型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在今年的新生中 長相名列前茅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然已經調查好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個勇美怎麼會對你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水收到情書耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,－他們的精神年齡幾歲啊\N-別這樣 快還我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都說別這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係 給我看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們玩夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛生氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 讓我們看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-快把他壓住\N-總之借我們看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全被拿來炒作了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟這可是個話題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過那真的是情書嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會有人惡作劇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這倒是有可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞 你已經吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您看了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是新井木？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正中直球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-勇美好厲害\N-好棒的告白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天的模擬訓練是4A嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要交往還是要拒絕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多也該講明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說 就是沒有交往的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過如果不明講的話 對她而言也是很可憐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法 我就傳授給他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不能外傳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個戀愛高手所創的\N「不傷害對方並拒絕」的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這種方法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧 聽清楚囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽咪～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽咪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法當面拒絕 就得讓她討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把自己的母親稱作媽咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有戀母情節 絕對會被討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這破壞力大概超過PBE了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是幻獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外還有別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如嘴裏碎碎念 假裝很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者說自己的興趣是編蕾絲等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有其他喜歡的女生 應該是最好的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畢竟是王道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-擊破數8\N-命中率55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中彈數0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這陣子狀況一直不太好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是因為那個原因嗎 最近速水身邊似乎很熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我要說的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村的數值下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請叫我勇美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水學長真會欺負人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欺負？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過學長 這禮拜天有空嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去看電影呢 我有兩張票喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看完電影之後 再去喝個茶吃晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到吃完飯之後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我…其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說你有其他喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰 學長喜歡的是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說這種讓人誤解的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會跟這種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學長不會喜歡那種人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水那傢伙結果如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約會是今天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像他那種人啊 一定是不好意思到底的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫新井木的女孩很積極喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反倒速水變成被動了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 新井木不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 要叫我勇美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過有一點我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是拒絕約會過一次嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定他真的有其他喜歡的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 聽到芝村時他還臉紅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼傻話 哪有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水他本人也否認啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞 你還要再洗一次嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說速水跟芝村啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩人之間或許有什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個姊姊我就不知道囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.03,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別來了 你一定什麼都知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要吝嗇 跟我們講啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事放著不管 遲早會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.58,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在去年的聖誕夜 速水跟芝村他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是兩個人獨處對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-這麼說來\N-那時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到聖誕夜時一對男女該做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有哪位知道會是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從沒想過你是累贅 我也不會丟下你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你沒去約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起、對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我道歉有什麼用啊 笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬼！惡魔！沒骨氣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全上壘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點 比賽要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以突然變冷淡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她叫新井木是吧 之前關係不是有所進展了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我後來沒有去約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問為什麼我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是出門了嗎 不然你在外面作什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.82,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一個人在街上晃 然後吃個飯 到書店去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不長進的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為這樣 我才放不下心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該要畫線囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的比賽要開始囉 快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事嗎 速水學長 你怎麼參加比賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒已經好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的好擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上你打電話來時\N不但一直咳嗽 聲音也沙啞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-聽說燒到40度 還拉肚子\N-感冒啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來至少還是有解釋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的沒有問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打者就位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-為什麼班長\N-為什麼我們就不能上場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來、我來～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-勇美\N-勇美沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.83,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把她…帶到保健室如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小志 不趕快的話 她會很痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-你還好吧\N-勇美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.68,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水學長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急廣播、緊急廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.16,0:17:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121部隊請盡速準備出擊 再次廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必須走了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}5121部隊請盡速準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實真的很痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有接吻嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦 你們真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-什麼嘛\N-真是無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水學長是要出擊 這可是要賭命的崇高使命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到這裏啊勇美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉 至今都沒有說那個人到底哪裏好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.06,0:18:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你中學就很崇拜駕駛員 會看新聞 調查各個部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼會是他啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員不是還有很多嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我就覺得瀨戶口學長不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是速水學長就不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們根本就不知道他的真實一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水厚志 戰士中的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.19,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極限之下的正確判斷力 還有不畏懼死亡的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重點是他無人能比的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他才是理想中的駕駛員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次搞得真是不得了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要幫寫領料單的人想想嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼了呢 速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 你也不像平常的你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 幸好兩人都沒受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你可得幫忙修理喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學長、速水學長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學長你沒事吧 有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有什麼我能做的 我想要幫學長的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學長 我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是個駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.79,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道何時會被召集 每次出動也不一定能平安回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我沒辦法跟你好好交往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡學長 我一直都很崇拜學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在去年的菊池縣攻防戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道學長在那場激戰擔任PBE的活躍事跡之後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在菊池戰並不是負責PBE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.11,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責菊池戰PBE的 記得是8331部隊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來 那邊的三號機的確也是雙人座機型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.06,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我認錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今發生的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你全部忘記吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今發生的事情 請你全部忘記吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來、原來她搞錯人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傑作
